HEADWORD: Haematachometer
<hw>Haem`a*ta*chom"e*ter</hw>
<pr>(-t⟦adot⟧*k⟦ocr⟧m"⟦esl⟧*t⟦etil⟧r)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos>
<ety>[<ets>Haema-</ets> + Gr. <grk>tachy`s</grk> swift +
<ets>-meter</ets>.]</ety> <fld>(Physiol.)</fld> <def>A form of apparatus
